# Android — Kotlin + Jetpack Compose

## Stack
- Kotlin, Jetpack Compose (BOM 2026.01.01), Hilt DI
- Retrofit 3 + kotlinx.serialization, OkHttp 4.12
- Room 2.8.4 (local DB), DataStore (token storage)
- Navigation Compose with type-safe routes
- Min SDK 29, Target SDK 35, Compile SDK 36

## Structure
```
app/src/main/kotlin/{{ package_identifier | replace('.', '/') }}/
  di/            → Hilt modules (AppModule)
  navigation/    → Screen routes, NavGraph
  data/remote/   → ApiService, AuthInterceptor
  data/local/    → TokenStorage (DataStore)
  data/local/db/ → Room: AppDatabase, DAOs, entities
  data/repository/ → Interface + Impl
  domain/model/  → DTOs (kotlinx.serialization)
  ui/theme/      → Material3 theme from design tokens
  ui/auth/       → LoginScreen + LoginViewModel
  ui/examples/   → ExampleListScreen + ExampleListViewModel
  ui/common/     → LoadingIndicator, ErrorView
```

## MVVM Pattern
- `@HiltViewModel` with `StateFlow<UiState>`
- `sealed interface UiState`: Idle, Loading, Success(data), Error(message)
- `@Composable` screens collect state via `collectAsState()`
- One ViewModel per screen, injected via `hiltViewModel()`

## Conventions
- Repositories: interface + Impl, bound in Hilt AppModule
- API base URL via `buildConfigField` in `build.gradle.kts`
- Room for local caching, DataStore for preferences/tokens
- Tests: MockK + Turbine for Flow testing
